name: Navy Trooper Shield Technician
Lore: 'Many Imperial Navy troopers receive technical as well as combat training, which they use to maintain the Empire''s military facilities.',
Text: 'Forfeit +2 while with Hewex. When at Bunker (or aboard a Star Destroyer at Endor), cumulatively adds 1 to deploy cost of each opponent''s starship and non-Ewok vehicle deploying to Endor (or to your mobile site orbiting Endor)',
